                            <decoNote>
                                <p>The lid, on which the inscription is placed, is carved in relief as a reclining
                                    man. He rests on his left side, with his head turned slightly to
                                    the right; his left leg lies flat against the mattress. Remzna
                                    wears a mantle draped across the lower part of his body. The jaw
                                    is emphasized, with a broad, prominent chin. His left hand lies
                                    in a relaxed pose on the cushions. The face is short and square
                                    in shape.</p>
